New_Brunswick.Cow Yard Brook (New Jersey):
The Cow Yard Brook is a small tributary of the Oakeys Brook, in central South Brunswick, New Jersey in the United States.


== Course ==
The Cow Yard Brook starts at 40°24′43″N 74°32′8″W near the intersection of Beekman Road, Northumberland Way, and Route 1. It crosses Deans Lane near its intersection with Black Horse Lane.
